    v1 = 0.80
    v0 = (v1 - (wp.sin(v2 + 0.49) - v2))
    v2 = v2
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.13 - tmp + 0.74) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.17)) * wp.abs((v1 + 0.97 - tmp + 0.16)))
